<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Email Verification Required</title>

  <style>
    body {
      background: #f0f3f8;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 35px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid #e0e4eb;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    }

    h2 {
      color: #1d3557;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 26px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    p {
      color: #444;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin: 12px 0;
    }

    .highlight {
      color: #1d3557;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .btn-wrapper {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 35px 0;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #1d3557;
      color: #fff !important;
      padding: 14px 30px;
      font-size: 17px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: 0.2s ease-in-out;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background: #16324a;
    }

    .note {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 40px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #7a7a7a;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>üîê Verify Your Email</h2>

    <p>Hi <span class="highlight"><%= name %></span>,</p>

    <p>
      Thank you for creating an account with us.  
      Before you can start using all features, we need to confirm your email address.
    </p>

    <p>Please click the button below to verify your account:</p>

    <div class="btn-wrapper">
      <a href="<%= verifyUrl %>" class="btn">Verify Email Now</a>
    </div>

    <p class="note">
      If you didn‚Äôt request this, you can safely ignore this email.
    </p>

    <div class="footer">
      ¬© <%= year %> MyApp ‚Äî All Rights Reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
